description:
'He predicted everything in this 98' interview"
In this video, we dive into Terence McKenna’s astonishing 1998 interview—filmed by John Hazard—where he outlines the very world we’re living in today. Every prediction he made back then has come true, and we’ll also explore what he believed is still yet to unfold.

Watch the full, uncut interview here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GdEKhIk-8Gg
